462 static bool CFARCADSP_isObjectDetectedOnDopplerLine
463 (
464  uint32_t dopplerIdx,
465  uint32_t numDopplerBins,
466  uint32_t numRangeBins,
467  uint32_t *cfarDetOutBitMask
468 )
469 {
470  uint32_t bit, word;
471  uint32_t bitIndex;
472  uint32_t rangeIdx;
473  bool detected = false;
474 
475  for(rangeIdx = 0; rangeIdx < numRangeBins;rangeIdx++)
476  {
477  bitIndex = rangeIdx * numDopplerBins + dopplerIdx;
478  word = bitIndex >> 5;
479  bit = bitIndex & 31;
480  if (cfarDetOutBitMask[word] & (1 << bit))
481  {
482  detected = true;
483  break;
484  }
485  }
486  return(detected);
487 }

577 static uint32_t CFARCADSP_peakGrouping
578 (
579  CFARCADspObj *cfarObj,
580  uint16_t numDetectedObjs
581 )
582 {
583  uint16_t detIdx;
584  uint16_t numPeakGrp = 0;
585  uint16_t index;
586  uint8_t scheme;
587 
588  if(cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.peakGroupingEn)
589  {
590  scheme = cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.peakGroupingScheme;
591  }
592  else
593  {
594  scheme = cfarObj->cfarCfgDoppler.peakGroupingScheme;
595  }
596 
597  if (scheme == DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_CFAR_PEAK_BASED)
598  {
599  numPeakGrp = mmwavelib_cfarPeakQualifiedInOrderPruning(cfarObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf, /* output the peak index after the group */
600  cfarObj->detObjRangeIdxBuf, /* raw detection range index */
601  cfarObj->detObjDopplerIdxBuf, /* raw detection doppler index */
602  cfarObj->detObjPeakValBuf, /* raw detection peak value */
603  numDetectedObjs, /* number of raw detection peaks */
604  cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins, /* number of doppler bins */
605  cfarObj->fovRange.maxIdx, /* maximum range bin */
606  cfarObj->fovRange.minIdx, /* minimum range bin */
607  cfarObj->cfarCfgDoppler.peakGroupingEn, /* doppler direction group */
608  cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.peakGroupingEn, /* range direction group */
609  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrListSize/* maximum grouped peaks */
610  );
611 
612  }
613  else if (scheme == DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_DET_MATRIX_BASED)
614  {
615  numPeakGrp = mmwavelib_cfarPeakPruning (cfarObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf,
616  cfarObj->detObjRangeIdxBuf, /* raw detection range index */
617  cfarObj->detObjDopplerIdxBuf, /* raw detection doppler index */
618  numDetectedObjs,
619  (uint16_t *)cfarObj->res.detMatrix.data,
620  cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins, /* number of doppler bins */
621  cfarObj->fovRange.maxIdx, /* maximum range bin */
622  cfarObj->fovRange.minIdx, /* minimum range bin */
623  cfarObj->cfarCfgDoppler.peakGroupingEn, /* doppler direction group */
624  cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.peakGroupingEn, /* range direction group */
625  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrListSize);
626  }
627  else
628  {
629  numPeakGrp = numDetectedObjs;
630  }
631 
632  /* Based on the detObjPeakIdxBuf, construct detection list */
633  for (index = 0; index < numPeakGrp; index ++)
634  {
635  float snrdB;
636 
637  detIdx = cfarObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf[index];
638  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[index].rangeIdx = cfarObj->detObjRangeIdxBuf[detIdx];
639  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[index].dopplerIdx = cfarObj->detObjDopplerIdxBuf[detIdx];
640  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[index].noise = cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[detIdx].noise;
641  snrdB = CFARCADSP_CONV_PEAK_TO_LOG((float)cfarObj->detObjPeakValBuf[detIdx], DPIF_DETMATRIX_DATA_QFORMAT) -
642  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[index].noise;
643  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[index].snr = (int16_t)snrdB;
644  }
645 
646  return(numPeakGrp);
647 }

665 static int32_t CFARCADSP_processDopplerDomain
666 (
667  CFARCADspObj *cfarObj,
668  uint8_t peakGrpingEn,
669  uint32_t *waitingTime,
670  int32_t *errCode
671 )
672 {
673  uint32_t numDetObjPerCfar;
674  uint32_t numDetObjDoppler = 0U;
675  uint32_t detIndex;
676  uint16_t rangeIdx;
677  volatile uint32_t startTimeWait;
678 
679  /* Trigger both ping and pong channel */
680  if ((*errCode = EDMA_startDmaTransfer(cfarObj->res.edmaHandle, cfarObj->res.edmaInPing.channel)) != EDMA_NO_ERROR)
681  {
682  goto exit;
683  }
684  if ((*errCode = EDMA_startDmaTransfer(cfarObj->res.edmaHandle, cfarObj->res.edmaInPong.channel)) != EDMA_NO_ERROR)
685  {
686  goto exit;
687  }
688 
689  memset (cfarObj->res.cfarDopplerDetOutBitMask, 0x0, cfarObj->res.cfarDopplerDetOutBitMaskSize * sizeof(uint32_t));
690 
691  /* Loop through all range bins for CFAR detection */
692  rangeIdx = 0;
693  do
694  {
695  uint16_t *currDetMatrixBuffer;
696  uint8_t edmaChannel;
697 
698  if(rangeIdx %2 == 0)
699  {
700  edmaChannel = cfarObj->res.edmaInPing.channel;
701  }
702  else
703  {
704  edmaChannel = cfarObj->res.edmaInPong.channel;
705  }
706 
707  /* Calculate current local buffer base address */
708  currDetMatrixBuffer = &cfarObj->res.localDetMatrixBuffer[cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins * (rangeIdx % 2)];
709 
710  /* Wait for EDMA transfer of current range line to complete */
711  startTimeWait = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp();
712  CFARCADSP_waitEDMATransComplete(cfarObj->res.edmaHandle, edmaChannel);
713  *waitingTime += Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp() - startTimeWait;
714 
715  /* CFAR-detecton on range line: search doppler peak among numDopplerBins samples */
716  numDetObjPerCfar = mmwavelib_cfarCadBwrap_wNoise(
717  currDetMatrixBuffer,
718  cfarObj->res.cfarDetOutBuffer,
719  cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins,
720  cfarObj->cfarCfgDoppler.thresholdScale,
721  cfarObj->cfarCfgDoppler.noiseDivShift,
722  cfarObj->cfarCfgDoppler.guardLen,
723  cfarObj->cfarCfgDoppler.winLen,
724  cfarObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf);
725 
726  for (detIndex = 0; detIndex < numDetObjPerCfar; detIndex++)
727  {
728  uint16_t dopplerIndex;
729  float noisedB;
730  dopplerIndex = cfarObj->res.cfarDetOutBuffer[detIndex];
731 
732  /* Update detection bit mask */
733  CFARCADSP_setCfarDetMaskLine(rangeIdx, dopplerIndex, cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins, cfarObj->res.cfarDopplerDetOutBitMask);
734 
735  /* Calculate noise and snr */
736  noisedB = CFARCADSP_CONV_PEAK_TO_LOG((float)cfarObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf[detIndex], DPIF_DETMATRIX_DATA_QFORMAT);
737 
738  if (cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.thresholdScale > 0)
739  {
740  /* If RangeDomain CFAR is enabld, no need to save detected objects */
741  }
742  else
743  {
744  if(peakGrpingEn)
745  {
746  cfarObj->detObjRangeIdxBuf[numDetObjDoppler] = rangeIdx;
747  cfarObj->detObjDopplerIdxBuf[numDetObjDoppler] = dopplerIndex;
748  cfarObj->detObjPeakValBuf[numDetObjDoppler] = currDetMatrixBuffer[dopplerIndex];
749  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjDoppler].noise = (int16_t)noisedB;
750  }
751  else
752  {
753  float snrdB;
754  snrdB = CFARCADSP_CONV_PEAK_TO_LOG((float)currDetMatrixBuffer[dopplerIndex], DPIF_DETMATRIX_DATA_QFORMAT) - noisedB;
755 
756  /* Update detection list */
757  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjDoppler].rangeIdx = rangeIdx;
758  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjDoppler].dopplerIdx= dopplerIndex;
759  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjDoppler].snr = snrdB;
760  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjDoppler].noise = (int16_t)noisedB;
761  }
762 
763  numDetObjDoppler ++;
764  if(numDetObjDoppler >= cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrListSize)
765  {
766  /* Output is limited by cfarRngDopSnrList size */
767  goto exit;
768  }
769  }
770  }
771  rangeIdx++;
772 
773  /* Trigger next EDMA if it is not the last range Bins */
774  if(rangeIdx < (cfarObj->staticCfg.numRangeBins - 1))
775  {
776  if ((*errCode = EDMA_startDmaTransfer(cfarObj->res.edmaHandle, edmaChannel)) != EDMA_NO_ERROR)
777  {
778  goto exit;
779  }
780  }
781  }while(rangeIdx < cfarObj->staticCfg.numRangeBins);
782 exit:
783  return numDetObjDoppler;
784 }

802 static int32_t CFARCADSP_processRangeDomain
803 (
804  CFARCADspObj *cfarObj,
805  uint8_t peakGrpingEn,
806  uint32_t *waitingTime,
807  uint32_t numDetObjDoppler
808 )
809 {
810  uint32_t detIdx;
811  uint32_t numDetObjIndex = 0;
812  volatile uint32_t startTimeWait;
813  uint32_t dopplerLine;
814  uint32_t numDetObj;
815  uint32_t srcAddr;
816  uint32_t localBufferAddr;
817  uint16_t loopIndex = 0;
818  uint16_t oneDopplerBinSize;
819  int16_t dopplerSgnIdx;
820 
821  oneDopplerBinSize = cfarObj->staticCfg.numRangeBins * sizeof(uint16_t);
822 
823  /* Starting from first dopplerLine */
824  dopplerLine = 0;
825 
826  do
827  {
828  /* Check if any bits are set for a particular doppler line */
829  if(CFARCADSP_isObjectDetectedOnDopplerLine(dopplerLine,
830  cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins,
831  cfarObj->staticCfg.numRangeBins,
832  cfarObj->res.cfarDopplerDetOutBitMask) == false)
833  {
834  /* No objects are found on doppler line , skip to next doppler line */
835  dopplerLine++;
836  continue;
837  }
838 
839  dopplerSgnIdx = dopplerLine;
840  if (dopplerSgnIdx >= (int32_t)(cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins>>1))
841  {
842  dopplerSgnIdx = dopplerSgnIdx - (int32_t)cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins;
843  }
844 
845  /* Calculate source address in detMatrix for a doppler Line with detected objects */
846  srcAddr = dopplerLine*sizeof(uint16_t) + (uint32_t)cfarObj->res.detMatrix.data;
847 
848  /* When loopIndex is even, use Ping buffer. Otherwise use pong buffer */
849  localBufferAddr = (uint32_t)cfarObj->res.localDetMatrixBuffer + (loopIndex %2) *oneDopplerBinSize;
850 
851  /* Setup EDMA to bring in detection matrix for the dopplerLine */
852  CFARCADSP_configEDMARangeDomain(cfarObj->res.edmaHandle,
853  &cfarObj->res.edmaInPing,
854  &cfarObj->staticCfg,
855  srcAddr,
856  localBufferAddr);
857 
858  if (( EDMA_startDmaTransfer(cfarObj->res.edmaHandle, cfarObj->res.edmaInPing.channel)) != EDMA_NO_ERROR)
859  {
860  goto exit;
861  }
862 
863  /* Wait for DMA transfer of current dopple line to complete */
864  startTimeWait = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp();
865  CFARCADSP_waitEDMATransComplete(cfarObj->res.edmaHandle, cfarObj->res.edmaInPing.channel);
866  *waitingTime += Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp() - startTimeWait;
867 
868  /* Do CFAR search for range peak among numRangeBins samples for the doppler line*/
869  numDetObj = mmwavelib_cfarCadB_SOGO_wNoise(
870  (uint16_t *)localBufferAddr,
871  cfarObj->res.cfarDetOutBuffer,
872  cfarObj->staticCfg.numRangeBins,
873  cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.averageMode,
874  cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.thresholdScale,
875  cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.noiseDivShift,
876  cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.guardLen,
877  cfarObj->cfarCfgRange.winLen,
878  cfarObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf);
879 
880  for(detIdx=0; detIdx <numDetObj; detIdx++)
881  {
882  if (numDetObjIndex < cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrListSize)
883  {
884  uint16_t rangeIdx;
885  uint16_t *cfarDetList = (uint16_t *)cfarObj->res.cfarDetOutBuffer;
886  uint16_t *detMat = (uint16_t *)localBufferAddr;
887 
888  rangeIdx = cfarDetList[detIdx];
889 
890  /* Is the object in Doppler Domain as well? */
891  if(CFARCADSP_isObjectDetected( rangeIdx,
892  dopplerLine,
893  cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins,
894  cfarObj->res.cfarDopplerDetOutBitMask) == false)
895  {
896  /* Object is not detected in Doppler domain, continue for next detected objects */
897  continue;
898  }
899 
900  if ((rangeIdx >= cfarObj->fovRange.minIdx) &&
901  (rangeIdx <= cfarObj->fovRange.maxIdx) &&
902  (dopplerSgnIdx >= cfarObj->fovDoppler.minIdx) &&
903  (dopplerSgnIdx <= cfarObj->fovDoppler.maxIdx))
904  {
905  float noisedB;
906 
907  /* Calculate noise */
908  noisedB = CFARCADSP_CONV_PEAK_TO_LOG((float)cfarObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf[detIdx], DPIF_DETMATRIX_DATA_QFORMAT);
909  if(peakGrpingEn)
910  {
911  cfarObj->detObjRangeIdxBuf[numDetObjIndex] = rangeIdx;
912  cfarObj->detObjDopplerIdxBuf[numDetObjIndex] = dopplerLine;
913  cfarObj->detObjPeakValBuf[numDetObjIndex] = detMat[rangeIdx];
914  }
915  else
916  {
917  float snrdB;
918 
919  snrdB = CFARCADSP_CONV_PEAK_TO_LOG((float)detMat[rangeIdx], DPIF_DETMATRIX_DATA_QFORMAT) - noisedB;
920 
921  /* Update detection list */
922  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjIndex].rangeIdx = rangeIdx;
923  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjIndex].dopplerIdx = dopplerLine;
924  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjIndex].snr = (int16_t)snrdB;
925  }
926  cfarObj->res.cfarRngDopSnrList[numDetObjIndex].noise = (int16_t)noisedB;
927 
928  numDetObjIndex++;
929  }
930  }
931  else
932  {
933  break;
934  }
935  }
936 
937  /* Current doppler line is completed , move on to next doppler line */
938  loopIndex++;
939  dopplerLine++;
940  }while(dopplerLine<cfarObj->staticCfg.numDopplerBins);
941 exit:
942  return(numDetObjIndex);
943 }

1004 int32_t DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_config
1005 (
1006  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Handle handle,
1007  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Config *cfarcaCfg
1008 )
1009 {
1010  int32_t retVal = 0;
1011  CFARCADspObj *cfarDspObj = (CFARCADspObj *)handle;
1012  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_HW_Resources *pRes = &cfarcaCfg->res;
1013  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_StaticConfig *staticCfg = &cfarcaCfg->staticCfg;
1014 
1015  if(cfarDspObj == NULL)
1016  {
1017  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1018  goto exit;
1019  }
1020 
1021  /* Validate buffer pointer */
1022  if( (pRes->localDetMatrixBuffer == NULL) ||
1023  (pRes->cfarDetOutBuffer == NULL) ||
1024  (pRes->cfarDopplerDetOutBitMask == NULL) ||
1025  (pRes->cfarRngDopSnrList == NULL) ||
1026  (pRes->detMatrix.data == NULL))
1027  {
1028  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL_EBUFFER_POINTER;
1029  goto exit;
1030  }
1031 
1032  /* Check if detection matrix format is supported. */
1033  if(pRes->detMatrix.datafmt != DPIF_DETMATRIX_FORMAT_1)
1034  {
1035  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL__DET_MATRIX_FORMAT;
1036  goto exit;
1037  }
1038 
1039  if MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(pRes->detMatrix.data,
1040  DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_DET_MATRIX_BYTE_ALIGNMENT)
1041  {
1042  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_DET_MATRIX;
1043  goto exit;
1044  }
1045 
1046  if MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(pRes->cfarRngDopSnrList,
1047  DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_CFAR_DET_LIST_BYTE_ALIGNMENT)
1048  {
1049  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_CFAR_DET_LIST;
1050  goto exit;
1051  }
1052 
1053  if MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(pRes->cfarDopplerDetOutBitMask,
1054  DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_DOPPLER_DET_OUT_BIT_MASK_BYTE_ALIGNMENT)
1055  {
1056  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_DOPPLER_DET_OUT_BIT_MASK;
1057  goto exit;
1058  }
1059 
1060  if MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(pRes->localDetMatrixBuffer,
1061  DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_DET_MATRIX_LOCAL_BYTE_ALIGNMENT)
1062  {
1063  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_LOCAL_DETMATRIX;
1064  goto exit;
1065  }
1066 
1067  if MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(pRes->cfarDetOutBuffer,
1068  DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_CFAR_DETOUT_BYTE_ALIGNMENT)
1069  {
1070  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_LOCAL_CFAR_DETOUT;
1071  goto exit;
1072  }
1073 
1074  if MEM_IS_NOT_ALIGN(pRes->cfarScrachBuffer,
1075  DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_SCRACHBUF_BYTE_ALIGNMENT)
1076  {
1077  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEMALIGN_SCRATCH_BUFFER;
1078  goto exit;
1079  }
1080 
1081  /* Check if input scratch memory for bit mask is sufficient */
1082  if ((pRes->cfarDopplerDetOutBitMaskSize * 32U) <
1083  (staticCfg->numDopplerBins * staticCfg->numRangeBins))
1084  {
1085  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEM__INSUFFICIENT_DOP_DET_OUT_BIT_MASK;
1086  goto exit;
1087  }
1088 
1089  /* Validating buffer size */
1090  if( (pRes->localDetMatrixBufferSize < MAX(staticCfg->numDopplerBins, staticCfg->numRangeBins) * sizeof(uint16_t) * 2U) ||
1091  (pRes->cfarDetOutBufferSize < MAX(staticCfg->numDopplerBins, staticCfg->numRangeBins) * sizeof(uint16_t)) ||
1092  (pRes->detMatrix.dataSize < staticCfg->numRangeBins * staticCfg->numDopplerBins * sizeof(uint16_t)))
1093  {
1094  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL_EBUFFER_SIZE;
1095  goto exit;
1096  }
1097 
1098  /* Validate peak grouping parameters */
1099  if(((cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgRange->peakGroupingEn) &&
1100  (cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgRange->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_DET_MATRIX_BASED)) &&
1101  (cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgRange->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_CFAR_PEAK_BASED))
1102  {
1103  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1104  goto exit;
1105  }
1106 
1107  if(((cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgDoppler->peakGroupingEn) &&
1108  (cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgDoppler->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_DET_MATRIX_BASED)) &&
1109  (cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgDoppler->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_CFAR_PEAK_BASED))
1110  {
1111  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1112  goto exit;
1113  }
1114 
1115  /* Validate CFAR guard/noise len */
1116  if ((cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgRange->guardLen + cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgRange->winLen) * 2U >= cfarcaCfg->staticCfg.numRangeBins)
1117  {
1118  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1119  goto exit;
1120  }
1121 
1122  /* Validate CFAR guard/noise len */
1123  if ((cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgDoppler->guardLen + cfarcaCfg->dynCfg.cfarCfgDoppler->winLen) * 2U >= cfarcaCfg->staticCfg.numDopplerBins)
1124  {
1125  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1126  goto exit;
1127  }
1128 
1129  CFARCADSP_saveConfiguration(cfarDspObj, cfarcaCfg);
1130 
1131  /* The scrach buffer will be used for peak grouping and cfar noise buffer */
1132  if((pRes->cfarScrachBuffer == NULL) ||
1133  (pRes->cfarScrachBufferSize < pRes->cfarRngDopSnrListSize * sizeof(uint16_t) * 4U ))
1134  {
1135  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_ENOMEM__INSUFFICIENT_SCRATCH_BUFFER;
1136  goto exit;
1137  }
1138  else
1139  {
1140  /* Internal scratch buffers for peak grouping and noise value */
1141  cfarDspObj->detObjRangeIdxBuf = (uint16_t *)pRes->cfarScrachBuffer;
1142  cfarDspObj->detObjDopplerIdxBuf = (uint16_t *)((uint32_t)pRes->cfarScrachBuffer + pRes->cfarRngDopSnrListSize * sizeof(uint16_t));
1143  cfarDspObj->detObjPeakValBuf = (uint16_t *)((uint32_t)cfarDspObj->detObjDopplerIdxBuf + pRes->cfarRngDopSnrListSize * sizeof(uint16_t));
1144  cfarDspObj->detObjPeakIdxBuf = (uint16_t *)((uint32_t)cfarDspObj->detObjPeakValBuf + pRes->cfarRngDopSnrListSize * sizeof(uint16_t));
1145  }
1146 
1147 exit:
1148  return retVal;
1149 }

1168 int32_t DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_process
1169 (
1170  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Handle handle,
1171  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_OutParams *outParams
1172 )
1173 {
1174  uint16_t numObjs = 0;
1175  int32_t retVal = 0;
1176  CFARCADspObj *cfarDspObj;
1177  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_HW_Resources *pRes;
1178  volatile uint32_t startTime;
1179  uint32_t waitTimeLocal = 0;
1180  uint8_t peakGrpingEn = 0;
1181 
1182  if (handle == NULL)
1183  {
1184  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1185  goto exit;
1186  }
1187 
1188  cfarDspObj = (CFARCADspObj *)handle;
1189  pRes = &cfarDspObj->res;
1190 
1191  if ( (cfarDspObj->cfarCfgRange.peakGroupingEn) || (cfarDspObj->cfarCfgDoppler.peakGroupingEn))
1192  {
1193  peakGrpingEn = 1;
1194  }
1195  startTime = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp();
1196 
1197  /* CFARCA Peak search along doppler line */
1198  if (cfarDspObj->cfarCfgDoppler.thresholdScale > 0)
1199  {
1200  /* Configure EDMA */
1201  retVal = CFARCADSP_configEDMADopplerDomain(pRes, &cfarDspObj->staticCfg);
1202  if (retVal != 0)
1203  {
1204  goto exit;
1205  }
1206 
1207  numObjs = CFARCADSP_processDopplerDomain(cfarDspObj, peakGrpingEn, &waitTimeLocal, &retVal);
1208  }
1209  else
1210  {
1211  /* All bit mask is masked in case of no-doppler domain detection */
1212  memset((void *)pRes->cfarDopplerDetOutBitMask, 0xFF, pRes->cfarDopplerDetOutBitMaskSize * sizeof(uint32_t));
1213  }
1214 
1215  /* CFARCA Peak search along range line*/
1216  if (cfarDspObj->cfarCfgRange.thresholdScale > 0)
1217  {
1218  numObjs = CFARCADSP_processRangeDomain(cfarDspObj, peakGrpingEn, &waitTimeLocal, numObjs);
1219  }
1220 
1221  if (numObjs > pRes->cfarRngDopSnrListSize)
1222  {
1223  numObjs = pRes->cfarRngDopSnrListSize;
1224  }
1225 
1226  /* CFARCA peak Grouping */
1227  if ( (cfarDspObj->cfarCfgRange.peakGroupingEn) || (cfarDspObj->cfarCfgDoppler.peakGroupingEn))
1228  {
1229  numObjs = CFARCADSP_peakGrouping(cfarDspObj, numObjs);
1230  }
1231 
1232  cfarDspObj->numProcess++;
1233 
1234  outParams->numCfarDetectedPoints = numObjs;
1235  outParams->stats.waitTime = waitTimeLocal;
1236  outParams->stats.processingTime = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp() - startTime - waitTimeLocal;
1237  outParams->stats.numProcess = cfarDspObj->numProcess;
1238 exit:
1239  return (retVal);
1240 }

1261 int32_t DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_control
1262 (
1263  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Handle handle,
1264  DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Cmd cmd,
1265  void *arg,
1266  uint32_t argSize
1267 )
1268 {
1269  int32_t retVal = 0;
1270  CFARCADspObj *cfarDspObj = (CFARCADspObj *)handle;
1271 
1272  /* Get rangeProc data object */
1273  if (cfarDspObj == NULL)
1274  {
1275  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1276  goto exit;
1277  }
1278 
1279  switch(cmd)
1280  {
1281  case DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Cmd_CfarRangeCfg:
1282  {
1283  DPU_CFARCAProc_CfarCfg *cfarcaCfg = arg;
1284  if((argSize != sizeof(DPU_CFARCAProc_CfarCfg)) ||
1285  (arg == NULL))
1286  {
1287  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1288  goto exit;
1289  }
1290  else if( (cfarcaCfg->peakGroupingEn) &&
1291  ((cfarcaCfg->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_DET_MATRIX_BASED) &&
1292  (cfarcaCfg->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_CFAR_PEAK_BASED)))
1293  {
1294  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1295  goto exit;
1296  }
1297  else
1298  {
1299  /* Save configuration */
1300  memcpy((void *)&cfarDspObj->cfarCfgRange, arg, argSize);
1301  CFARCADSP_adjustCfarCfg(&cfarDspObj->cfarCfgRange);
1302  }
1303  }
1304  break;
1305  case DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Cmd_CfarDopplerCfg:
1306  {
1307  DPU_CFARCAProc_CfarCfg *cfarcaCfg = arg;
1308  if((argSize != sizeof(DPU_CFARCAProc_CfarCfg)) ||
1309  (arg == NULL))
1310  {
1311  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1312  goto exit;
1313  }
1314  else if( (cfarcaCfg->peakGroupingEn) &&
1315  ((cfarcaCfg->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_DET_MATRIX_BASED) &&
1316  (cfarcaCfg->peakGroupingScheme != DPU_CFAR_PEAK_GROUPING_CFAR_PEAK_BASED)))
1317  {
1318  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1319  goto exit;
1320  }
1321  else
1322  {
1323  /* Save configuration */
1324  memcpy((void *)&cfarDspObj->cfarCfgDoppler, arg, argSize);
1325  /* DPU assumes that Doppler is always CFAR-CA but following code
1326  is added for generality */
1327  CFARCADSP_adjustCfarCfg(&cfarDspObj->cfarCfgDoppler);
1328  }
1329  }
1330  break;
1331  case DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Cmd_FovRangeCfg:
1332  {
1333  if((argSize != sizeof(DPU_CFARCAProc_FovCfg)) ||
1334  (arg == NULL))
1335  {
1336  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1337  goto exit;
1338  }
1339  else
1340  {
1341  /* Save configuration */
1342  CFARCADSP_fovConvertRange(arg,
1343  cfarDspObj->staticCfg.rangeStep,
1344  &cfarDspObj->fovRange);
1345  }
1346  }
1347  break;
1348  case DPU_CFARCAProcDSP_Cmd_FovDopplerCfg:
1349  {
1350  if((argSize != sizeof(DPU_CFARCAProc_FovCfg)) ||
1351  (arg == NULL))
1352  {
1353  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1354  goto exit;
1355  }
1356  else
1357  {
1358  /* Save configuration */
1359  CFARCADSP_fovConvertDoppler(arg,
1360  cfarDspObj->staticCfg.dopplerStep,
1361  &cfarDspObj->fovDoppler);
1362  }
1363  }
1364  break;
1365 
1366  default:
1367  retVal = DPU_CFARCAPROCDSP_EINVAL;
1368  break;
1369  }
1370 exit:
1371  return (retVal);
1372 }
